manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Minlu 3-in-1 Multi USB Charging Cable 3.0A ● The durability you’ve come to expect from Minlu 3-in-1 Charger Cord—now with universal compatibility. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fast Charging Solution
reviews.reviewText: The Minlu Multi Charging Cable has become an essential gadget in my daily life, making charging multiple devices a breeze. This versatile 3-in-1 retractable charging cord has impressed me with its durability, fast charging capabilities, and convenience.The first thing that caught my attention was the compact and portable design. The retractable cable neatly coils into a small and lightweight package, making it easy to carry around in my bag or pocket. It eliminates the mess of tangled cords, and I no longer need to carry multiple cables for different devices.The cable is 4 feet long, which gives me ample reach when charging my devices, even if the power outlet is far from where I'm sitting or standing. The length is just right for use at home, in the office, or when traveling.The 3-in-1 design offers three different connectors - USB Type-C, Micro USB, and Lightning - all in one cable. It's compatible with various devices, including smartphones, tablets, Bluetooth headphones, and more. I can conveniently charge my iPhone, Android phone, and Bluetooth earbuds with a single cable.The charging speed is impressive, supporting up to 3A fast charging. I've noticed that my devices charge faster compared to using other generic cables. It's a time-saver, especially when I'm in a rush and need to juice up my gadgets quickly.The build quality of the cable is excellent, with sturdy connectors and a durable cord that resists wear and tear. I appreciate that the connectors fit snugly into my devices without any loose connections.One of the standout features is the auto-locking mechanism. It allows me to adjust the length of the cable according to my needs and locks it in place, preventing it from recoiling when I'm charging my devices.In conclusion, the Minlu Multi Charging Cable has exceeded my expectations and made charging multiple devices a seamless experience. Its portability, fast charging capabilities, and compatibility with various devices make it a top-notch charging solution. I highly recommend this cable to anyone looking for a reliable and convenient charging cord for their everyday needs.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Versatile and Actually Works
reviews.reviewText: Loved the tri-head and tangle-free design. The retraction has not broken with normal wear and tear use. It will be one of my favorite products that I buy when I need a new charger or someone needs one as a gift. It's super convinent for company use when they have different phones that require different designs. It doesn't charge as fast as the apple charger cord + block, but that's not an issue for my use. It does seem to heat up my phone a little bit more than I would like, but not typically to the point where my phone stops charging.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Not all of the plugs work independently
reviews.reviewText: Only the iPhone charger works independently. The rest of the charger heads only work if my iPhone is also plugged in. I like this for my car since the cord length is adjustable. It also gives options for non-Apple passengers.
